timelineItems.desc: Two teams in a desperate chase for postseason positions in the Western Conference meet when Real Salt Lake play host to Seattle Sounders FC on Saturday evening at Rio Tinto Stadium.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: Real Salt Lake vs. Seattle Sounders FC | August 22, 2015

timelineItems.name: Daniel Haslam
timelineItems.text: 19' | GOAL RSL! They lead 2-0 over Seattle! #RSLvSEA http://t.co/Y82FxvHIfb

timelineItems.name: Heath Waddingham
timelineItems.text: 19': Mulholland's rocket hits the crossbar, but takes Frei out of the play. Jaime cleans up with a header! #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Jeremy Horton
timelineItems.text: Mulholland rocks a shot from distance off the crossbar, rebound falls to Jaime, he heads it past Frei who had dove out of the play. 2-0 #RSL

timelineItems.name: Loves Ideas
timelineItems.text: We need a #sounders end of game miracle please.

timelineItems.name: Doug Allen
timelineItems.text: #RSL was on point tonight. #RSLTID #RSLvSEA #BurritoWatch

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: There it is. Playoffs still in reach with the 2-0 victory over the Sounders. Just what the team needed. #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Chalupa Batman
timelineItems.text: You know what, I don't care to if #Burrito never plays a minute for #RSL as long as we win all our games like this.

timelineItems.name: Joe Tansey
timelineItems.text: Playoff desperation began to sink in this week in #MLS. #RSL, #Quakes74 & #DOOP responded with wins. Could be a wild finish to season.

timelineItems.name: Travis Cain
timelineItems.text: “You came a long way just to lose” it’s been sooo long since I’ve heard this song. #RSL

timelineItems.name: Andrew Martonik
timelineItems.text: That was... Not convincing from Sounders. #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Dustin Hughes
timelineItems.text: Winning feels so good #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Heath Waddingham
timelineItems.text: Passes: #RSL 442/533 (82%), Sounders 289/377 (76%). #WOW #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Heath Waddingham
timelineItems.text: And @javi_mo11 at a BLISTERING 81/88 passing, 3 key passes, 4 shots, 1 goal. #MOTM #RSLvSEA

timelineItems.name: Daniel Haslam
timelineItems.text: FT | @RealSaltLake pulls off the HUGE win over @SoundersFC. Final score: 2-0! #RSLvSEA http://t.co/oEM6eiWbop
